Package monniasza.collects.alloc

Class SimpleAllocator<T extends AllocationListener<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • monniasza.collects.alloc.SimpleAllocator<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - An implementation of the allocator. Exceptions thrown by listeners are forwarded to the exceptionHandler object in this allocator The exceptionHandler by default forwards exceptions to the thread's current UncaughtExceptionHandler, where thread is the thread used to run listeners
    All Implemented Interfaces:
